de.oaam.model.oaam.capabilities

Interface CapabilitiesContainerA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Capabilities, Subcapability
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CapabilitiesContainerAImpl, CapabilitiesImpl, SubcapabilityImpl

    public interface CapabilitiesContainerA
extends ElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. The root of the capabilities mode.

    The following features are supported:

    • Function Capabilties
    • Signal Capabilities
    • Device Capabilities
    • Sub Device Capabilities
    • Connection Capabilities
    • Subcapabilities
    See Also:
    CapabilitiesPackage.getCapabilitiesContainerA()
